snippet.title: Haunted House - Official Launch Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Creep, sneak, and dash your way through hordes of ghouls and eerie ectoplasms in this roguelite reimagining of the classic Atari adventure!
Haunted House Haunted House is available now for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, Nintendo Switch, Atari VCS, and PC.
